  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SinaRun</strong> is a momentum-based platforming and speedrunning game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal? Simply make the best time! What makes you different from the other players is not the cheap abilities you can get on the playground. It's how good you'll be at finding the best route, optimizing your jumps and sharpening your turns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a level you love, run it hundreds of times, and maybe, just maybe, claim the top spot on the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/324470/extras/f1a57583f8058300151bca70425c9c88.poster.avif?t=1762266472\" width=1170 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/324470/extras/f1a57583f8058300151bca70425c9c88.webm?t=1762266472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/324470/extras/f1a57583f8058300151bca70425c9c88.mp4?t=1762266472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16+ Levels with multiple paths. Finding a good route is the first step toward a good time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Leaderboards (Beat your friends or compete in the global leaderboard)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music by General Fuzz</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SinaRun</strong> is a momentum-based platforming and speedrunning game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal? Simply make the best time! What makes you different from the other players is not the cheap abilities you can get on the playground. It's how good you'll be at finding the best route, optimizing your jumps and sharpening your turns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a level you love, run it hundreds of times, and maybe, just maybe, claim the top spot on the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/324470/extras/f1a57583f8058300151bca70425c9c88.poster.avif?t=1762266472\" width=1170 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/324470/extras/f1a57583f8058300151bca70425c9c88.webm?t=1762266472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/324470/extras/f1a57583f8058300151bca70425c9c88.mp4?t=1762266472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16+ Levels with multiple paths. Finding a good route is the first step toward a good time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Leaderboards (Beat your friends or compete in the global leaderboard)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music by General Fuzz</p></li></ul>",
